e02cc44c8ad9dd61c9b80684b8cf5b64477a6fd6221cde9efea2a7594c6e7ce01a51f8bd4b80d72f82f7caf93217979fb0b354c420983891fa93f34c4252a035  0001-abuild-add-env-option-to-require-tests.patch"
